    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入我们官方社区Q群：471565221</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在名为弦域的高纬宇宙中探索一个又一个的神秘星系，这些星系有着自己的特殊的文明与丰富的资源，发现并试着在危险的星域生 存下来建立自己的据点，采集、运输、制造、提升自身天赋与科技，与敌对势力作战，与异星生物作战，获得他们的数据，研究并培养，使自己的束核舰进化为更高阶的座驾从而前往更危险的星域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070430/extras/3c087a5da218bf2ecd977ba1fa1344e1.avif?t=1770723976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070430/extras_big/3c087a5da218bf2ecd977ba1fa1344e1.webp?t=1770723976 width=1560 height=929 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  探索各种神秘的星域，它们有着独特的丰富资源，废弃的巨构残骸，隐藏在环带上的隐秘哨所，哪些等待您去发现的场景和秘密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070430/extras/1a47be2e3d148b1e0e6d601cb4f77acf.avif?t=1770723976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070430/extras_big/1a47be2e3d148b1e0e6d601cb4f77acf.webp?t=1770723976 width=1560 height=929 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现、采集、带回方舟生态舱加工、制造解锁不同副职业的天赋，解锁更高科技的制造配方与材料</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070430/extras/27d0b1bb2861cfd62319d5c6a2f7e034.avif?t=1770723976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070430/extras_big/27d0b1bb2861cfd62319d5c6a2f7e034.webp?t=1770723976 width=1560 height=929 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个星系都有独特的太空环境，发现不同势力的星际舰船或是诡异什么的异星生物，你还能在你感兴趣的地方建造一个据点，守护自己的据点或将它作为你跃迁的航标</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070430/extras/a57e730b4b8fce82ce9dfae439f8000f.avif?t=1770723976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070430/extras_big/a57e730b4b8fce82ce9dfae439f8000f.webp?t=1770723976 width=1560 height=929 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这充满未知的星域中所遇到的一切，都会让你有更美妙的体验与选着，作为星际独狼还是与他人组队探索、发现、挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
